Package: term-pcl
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Terminal point cloud visualizer
 term-pcl is a command-line point cloud visualizer for Linux terminals.
 It loads PCD, PLY, XYZ, XYZN, XYZRGB, and native termcloud indexes,
 then renders them using an interactive terminal UI.
